@startuml SSE Organization

actor User
control "Frontend\n(Axios + TypeScript)" as Frontend
control "Backend\n(Fastify + TypeScript)" as Backend
boundary "Event Bus\n(EventEmitter3)" as EventBus
participant "System" as System

== Establishing Connection ==
User -> Frontend: Initiate SSE connection
Frontend -> Backend: HTTP GET /events (SSE endpoint)
Backend -> Frontend: Set headers:\nContent-Type: text/event-stream\nCache-Control: no-cache\nConnection: keep-alive
Backend -> Frontend: Send initial message:\ndata: Connected\n\n
Frontend -> User: Connection established

== Sending Events ==
System -> EventBus: Fire event with data
EventBus -> Backend: Emit event with data
Backend -> Frontend: Send event over SSE:\ndata: { "message": "Hello, world!" }\n\n
Frontend -> User: Display received data

== Handling Disconnection ==
User -> Frontend: Close SSE connection
Frontend -> Backend: Close HTTP connection
Backend -> EventBus: Stop listening for events
Backend -> Frontend: Clean up resources

@enduml